{"id":817,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":817,"title":"Jeremiah 48","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 48"],[".studySummary",["i","Judgment and destruction will come upon the Moabites for their contempt of God."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.1","order":"02.25.048.53965"},["b","1"],"Against",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Moab"],"thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, the God of Israel; Woe unto Nebo! for it is spoiled: Kiriathaim is confounded",["i","and"],"taken: Misgab is confounded and dismayed."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.2","order":"02.25.048.53966"},["b","2"],["i","There shall be"],"no more praise of Moab: in Heshbon they have devised evil against it; come, and let us cut it off from",["i","being"],"a nation. Also thou shalt be cut down, O Madmen; the sword shall pursue thee."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.3","order":"02.25.048.53967"},["b","3"],"A voice of crying",["i","shall be"],"from",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Horonaim"],", spoiling and great destruction."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.4","order":"02.25.048.53968"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Moab"],"is destroyed; her little ones have caused a cry to be heard."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.5","order":"02.25.048.53969"},["b","5"],"For in the going up of Luhith continual weeping shall go up; for in the going down of Horonaim the enemies have heard a cry of destruction."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.6","order":"02.25.048.53970"},["b","6"],"Flee, save your lives, and be like the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"heath"],"in the wilderness."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.7","order":"02.25.048.53971"},["b","7"],"¶For because thou hast trusted in thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"works"],"and in thy treasures, thou shalt also be taken: and Chemosh shall go forth into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"captivity"],["i","with"],"his priests and his princes together."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.8","order":"02.25.048.53972"},["b","8"],"And the spoiler shall come upon every city, and no city shall escape: the valley also shall perish, and the plain shall be destroyed, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath spoken."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.9","order":"02.25.048.53973"},["b","9"],"Give wings unto Moab, that it may flee and get away: for the cities thereof shall be desolate, without any to dwell therein."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.10","order":"02.25.048.53974"},["b","10"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Cursed"],["i","be"],"he that doeth the work of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"deceitfully, and cursed",["i","be"],"he that keepeth back his sword from blood."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.11","order":"02.25.048.53975"},["b","11"],"¶Moab hath been at ease from his youth, and he hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"settled"],"on his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"lees"],", and hath not been emptied from vessel to vessel, neither hath he gone into captivity: therefore his taste remained in him, and his scent is not changed."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.12","order":"02.25.048.53976"},["b","12"],"Therefore, behold, the days come, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that I will send unto him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"wanderers"],", that shall cause him to wander, and shall empty his vessels, and break their bottles."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.13","order":"02.25.048.53977"},["b","13"],"And Moab shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"ashamed"],"of Chemosh, as the house of Israel was ashamed of Beth-el their confidence."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.14","order":"02.25.048.53978"},["b","14"],"¶How say ye, We",["i","are"],"mighty and strong men for the war?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.15","order":"02.25.048.53979"},["b","15"],"Moab is spoiled, and gone up",["i","out of"],"her cities, and his chosen young men are gone down to the slaughter, saith the King, whose name",["i","is"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.16","order":"02.25.048.53980"},["b","16"],"The calamity of Moab",["i","is"],"near to come, and his affliction hasteth fast."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.17","order":"02.25.048.53981"},["b","17"],"All ye that are about him, bemoan him; and all ye that know his name, say, How is the strong staff broken,",["i","and"],"the beautiful rod!"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.18","order":"02.25.048.53982"},["b","18"],"Thou daughter that dost inhabit Dibon, come down from",["i","thy"],"glory, and sit in thirst; for the spoiler of Moab shall come upon thee,",["i","and"],"he shall destroy thy strong holds."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.19","order":"02.25.048.53983"},["b","19"],"O inhabitant of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Aroer"],", stand by the way, and espy; ask him that fleeth, and her that escapeth,",["i","and"],"say, What is done?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.20","order":"02.25.048.53984"},["b","20"],"Moab is confounded; for it is broken down:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"howl"],"and cry; tell ye it in Arnon, that Moab is spoiled,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.21","order":"02.25.048.53985"},["b","21"],"And judgment is come upon the plain country; upon Holon, and upon Jahazah, and upon Mephaath,"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.22","order":"02.25.048.53986"},["b","22"],"And upon Dibon, and upon Nebo, and upon Beth-diblathaim,"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.23","order":"02.25.048.53987"},["b","23"],"And upon Kiriathaim, and upon Beth-gamul, and upon Beth-meon,"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.24","order":"02.25.048.53988"},["b","24"],"And upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Kerioth"],", and upon",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"Bozrah"],", and upon all the cities of the land of Moab, far or near."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.25","order":"02.25.048.53989"},["b","25"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"horn"],"of Moab is cut off, and his arm is broken, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.26","order":"02.25.048.53990"},["b","26"],"¶Make ye him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"drunken"],": for he magnified",["i","himself"],"against the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": Moab also shall wallow in his vomit, and he also shall be in derision."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.27","order":"02.25.048.53991"},["b","27"],"For was not Israel a derision unto thee? was he found among thieves? for since thou spakest of him, thou skippedst for joy."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.28","order":"02.25.048.53992"},["b","28"],"O ye that dwell in Moab, leave the cities, and dwell in the rock, and be like the dove",["i","that"],"maketh her nest in the sides of the hole’s mouth."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.29","order":"02.25.048.53993"},["b","29"],"We have heard the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"pride"],"of Moab, (he is exceeding proud) his loftiness, and his arrogancy, and his pride, and the haughtiness of his heart."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.30","order":"02.25.048.53994"},["b","30"],"I know his wrath, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; but",["i","it shall"],"not",["i","be"],"so; his lies shall not so effect",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.31","order":"02.25.048.53995"},["b","31"],"Therefore will I howl for Moab, and I will cry out for all Moab;",["i","mine heart"],"shall mourn for the men of Kir-heres."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.32","order":"02.25.048.53996"},["b","32"],"O vine of Sibmah, I will weep for thee with the weeping of Jazer: thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"plants"],"are gone over the sea, they reach",["i","even"],"to the sea of Jazer: the spoiler is fallen upon thy summer fruits and upon thy vintage."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.33","order":"02.25.048.53997"},["b","33"],"And joy and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"gladness"],"is taken from the plentiful field, and from the land of Moab; and I have caused wine to fail from the winepresses: none shall tread with shouting;",["i","their"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"shouting"],["i","shall be"],"no shouting."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.34","order":"02.25.048.53998"},["b","34"],"From the cry of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"Heshbon"],["i","even"],"unto Elealeh,",["i","and even"],"unto Jahaz, have they uttered their voice, from Zoar",["i","even"],"unto Horonaim,",["i","as"],"an heifer of three years old: for the waters also of Nimrim shall be desolate."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.35","order":"02.25.048.53999"},["b","35"],"Moreover I will cause to cease in Moab, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", him that offereth in the high places, and him that burneth incense to his gods."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.36","order":"02.25.048.54000"},["b","36"],"Therefore mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"heart"],"shall sound for Moab like pipes, and mine heart shall sound like",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"pipes"],"for the men of Kir-heres: because the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_36c"},"riches"],["i","that"],"he hath gotten are perished."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.37","order":"02.25.048.54001"},["b","37"],"For every head",["i","shall be"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"bald"],", and every beard clipped: upon all the hands",["i","shall be"],"cuttings, and upon the loins sackcloth."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.38","order":"02.25.048.54002"},["b","38"],["i","There shall be"],"lamentation generally upon all the housetops of Moab, and in the streets thereof: for I have broken Moab like a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"vessel"],"wherein",["i","is"],"no pleasure, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.39","order":"02.25.048.54003"},["b","39"],"They shall howl,",["i","saying,"],"How is it broken down! how hath Moab turned the back with shame! so shall Moab be a derision and a dismaying to all them about him."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.40","order":"02.25.048.54004"},["b","40"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Behold, he shall fly as an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"eagle"],", and shall spread his wings over Moab."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.41","order":"02.25.048.54005"},["b","41"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"Kerioth"],"is taken, and the strong holds are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_41b"},"surprised"],", and the mighty men’s hearts in Moab at that day shall be as the heart of a woman in her pangs."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.42","order":"02.25.048.54006"},["b","42"],"And Moab shall be destroyed from",["i","being"],"a people, because he hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"magnified"],["i","himself"],"against the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.43","order":"02.25.048.54007"},["b","43"],"Fear, and the pit, and the snare,",["i","shall be"],"upon thee, O inhabitant of Moab, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.44","order":"02.25.048.54008"},["b","44"],"He that fleeth from the fear shall fall into the pit; and he that getteth up out of the pit shall be taken in the snare: for I will bring upon it,",["i","even"],"upon Moab, the year of their visitation, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.45","order":"02.25.048.54009"},["b","45"],"They that fled stood under the shadow of Heshbon because of the force: but a fire shall come forth out of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_45a"},"Heshbon"],", and a flame from the midst of Sihon, and shall devour the corner of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_45b"},"Moab"],", and the crown of the head of the tumultuous ones."],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.46","order":"02.25.048.54010"},["b","46"],"Woe be unto thee, O Moab! the people of Chemosh perisheth: for thy sons are taken captives, and thy daughters captives."],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.47","order":"02.25.048.54011"},["b","47"],"¶Yet will I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_47a"},"bring again"],"the captivity of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_47b"},"Moab"],"in the latter days, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". Thus far",["i","is"],"the judgment of Moab."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.1a","order":"02.25.048.54012"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.21"},"Jer. 25:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.3a","order":"02.25.048.54014"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/15.5"},"Isa. 15:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.4a","order":"02.25.048.54016"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/15.1"},"Isa. 15:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.6a","order":"02.25.048.54018"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/17.6"},"Jer. 17:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.7a","order":"02.25.048.54020"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.29"},"Mosiah 12:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.7b","order":"02.25.048.54022"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/43.12"},"Jer. 43:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.3"},"49:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.10a","order":"02.25.048.54024"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.11a","order":"02.25.048.54026"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"relaxed his guard."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.11b","order":"02.25.048.54028"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.12"},"Zeph. 1:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.12a","order":"02.25.048.54030"},["b","12a"],["span.small","HEB"],"tilters (those who empty things out)."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.13a","order":"02.25.048.54032"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.6"},"Hosea 10:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.19a","order":"02.25.048.54034"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/2.36"},"Deut. 2:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.20a","order":"02.25.048.54036"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/16.7"},"Isa. 16:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.24a","order":"02.25.048.54038"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.41"},"Jer. 48:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.24b","order":"02.25.048.54040"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.13"},"Jer. 49:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.25a","order":"02.25.048.54042"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/75.10"},"Ps. 75:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.26a","order":"02.25.048.54044"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.27"},"Jer. 25:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.29a","order":"02.25.048.54046"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pride"},"TG Pride"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.32a","order":"02.25.048.54048"},["b","32a"],["span.small","HEB"],"branches."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.33a","order":"02.25.048.54050"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/16.10"},"Isa. 16:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.33b","order":"02.25.048.54052"},["b","33b"],["span.small","OR"],"cheering."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.34a","order":"02.25.048.54054"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/15.4"},"Isa. 15:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.36a","order":"02.25.048.54056"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/15.5"},"Isa. 15:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/16.11"},"16:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"36b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.36b","order":"02.25.048.54058"},["b","36b"],["span.small","OR"],"flutes."],["div",{"id":"36c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.36c","order":"02.25.048.54060"},["b","36c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.31.18,31,33"},"Hel. 13:31 (18, 31, 33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.37a","order":"02.25.048.54062"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/15.2"},"Isa. 15:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.38a","order":"02.25.048.54064"},["b","38a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/31.12"},"Ps. 31:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.28"},"Jer. 22:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/8.8"},"Hosea 8:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"40a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.40a","order":"02.25.048.54066"},["b","40a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/17.3"},"Ezek. 17:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"41a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.41a","order":"02.25.048.54068"},["b","41a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.24"},"Jer. 48:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"41b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.41b","order":"02.25.048.54070"},["b","41b"],["span.small","HEB"],"captured."],["div",{"id":"42a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.42a","order":"02.25.048.54072"},["b","42a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/2.8.8,10"},"Zeph. 2:8 (8, 10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"45a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.45a","order":"02.25.048.54074"},["b","45a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/21.28"},"Num. 21:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"45b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.45b","order":"02.25.048.54076"},["b","45b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.17"},"Num. 24:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"47a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.47a","order":"02.25.048.54078"},["b","47a"],["span.small","OR"],"turn away, remove."],["div",{"id":"47b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.47b","order":"02.25.048.54080"},["b","47b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/16.5.1-5"},"Isa. 16:5 (1–5)"],"."]]}
